rstanding, I wouldn=E2=80=99t even need money,=E2=80=9D but surely no one h=
ere believes that.[5] The Uniform Law Commission, which writes laws like th=
is for state legislatures to enact, has renamed the latest version of this =
one the =E2=80=9CUniform Voidable Transactions Act.=E2=80=9D But everyone s=
ays =E2=80=9Cfraudulent transfer,=E2=80=9D not =E2=80=9Cvoidable transactio=
n,=E2=80=9D and in any case the UVTA version is less widely adopted than th=
