-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt;">
<h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial=
, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">E for Extortion</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Leon Black, the former head of Apollo =
Global Management Inc., allegedly had an extramarital affair with a woman 3=
0 years younger than him, paid her millions of dollars during their sexual =
relationship, secretly recorded their conversations, and=C2=A0spent million=
s more dollars to conceal the affair from the directors and clients of his =
firm. When I say =E2=80=9Callegedly=E2=80=9D I mean that=E2=80=99s what=C2=
=A0<em>he=C2=A0</em>alleges; <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness=
.com/click/24503919.260023/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGlj=
bGVzLzIwMjEtMDctMTkvbGVvbi1ibGFjay1yZXZlYWxzLWludGltYXRlLWRldGFpbHMtaW4tZGV=
uaWFsLW9mLXNleHVhbC1hc3NhdWx0/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBf889f0db" itemprop=
=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decora=
tion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0000=
00; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> that=E2=80=99s hi=
s=C2=A0<em>defense=C2=A0</em>of his actions</a>.=C2=A0<em>Her=C2=A0</em>all=
egations are much worse; she claims that he abused and assaulted her and th=
en threatened her to keep her silent. He claims that she is lying and that =
she has been extorting money out of him for years.</p><p style=3D"margin: 1=
6px 0;">In any case they seem to agree that, after their affair ended, they=
 had lunch at the Four Seasons in 2015 and signed a contract providing that=
 Black would pay her $100,000 a month for 15 years. Here is an amazing deta=
il from <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24503919.2=
60023/aHR0cHM6Ly9pYXBwcy5jb3VydHMuc3RhdGUubnkudXMvbnlzY2VmL1ZpZXdEb2N1bWVud=
D9kb2NJbmRleD1TX1BMVVNfYjc0bW5vbm5aYVJaZDU2NERhYnc9PQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a=
23cBe0e346d4" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color=
: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bord=
er-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #cc=
c;">Black=E2=80=99s court filing</a>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16=
px 0;">After the parties entered into the Agreement, Mr. Black set up a new=
 account from which to make the monthly payments to Ganieva, which he calle=
d =E2=80=9CE Trust.=E2=80=9D In her Complaint, Ganieva states that she =E2=
=80=9Chas no knowledge as to why payments began from the =E2=80=98E Trust=
=E2=80=99 or what it is.=E2=80=9D (Cplt. =C2=B6 73). To be very clear: the =
=E2=80=9CE=E2=80=9D in =E2=80=9CE Trust=E2=80=9D stands for =E2=80=9CExtort=
ion.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I =E2=80=A6=C2=
=A0wow, okay. We talk from <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.c=
